   <div>
    <pb n="41"/>
    <opener index="false">
     * 44.
     <name placement="text" ref="1661" type="person">
      Болтон Голлу (Bolton Hall)
     </name>
     .1897 г. Марта 2. Никольское.
    </opener>
    <p id="42a390b4-693d-4be2-a732-6b20f2ddc4d4" rend="Obrashenie">
     Dear Sir,
    </p>
    <p id="83cce123-4fdd-4cdc-b013-9f578e55a2d2">
     I have received Your book
     <hi>
      1
     </hi>
     and have read it. I think it is very good and renders in a concise form quite truly the chief ideas of my book. I hope that this book in this new form will be usefull, in the sense in which I intented it to be, to a larger public than
     <hi style="opdelimiter">
      original.
     </hi>
    </p>
    <p id="efd709c3-e2bb-4884-bf6d-8f51a198e84e">
     <pb n="42"/>
     <hi style="npdelimiter">
      With
     </hi>
     my best thanks and wishes for the success of Your book, I am, dear Sir,
    </p>
    <p id="90f19330-e093-4146-bf2d-931b9f634f36" rend="right">
     Yours truly.
    </p>
    <noteGrp type="comments"/>
   </div>
